notes: 48 PubMed results. No RCT adding isolated CBD on top of nabiximols found. Results are nabiximols-alone trials and reviews. Nabiximols already contains CBD — independent combination study does not exist. Null search Feb 27, 2026.

22 PubMed results. No RCT augmenting nabiximols with additional THC found. Nabiximols already contains THC (Sativex = THC:CBD 1:1) — pairing with isolated THC is structurally redundant. Flagged invalid Feb 27, 2026.

Karschner et al., Clin Pharmacol Ther 2011 (randomized crossover N=9). Oral dronabinol vs. nabiximols head-to-head. Finding: pharmacodynamically equivalent at therapeutic doses — no substantial CBD-induced modulation of THC's effects. Comparative equivalence design, NOT additive co-administration. Effect size set conservatively low (0.30). Feb 27, 2026.

26 PubMed results. No combination-specific human RCT or quantitative co-administration trial found. Results are reviews, preclinical, and analytical/formulation studies only. Null search Feb 27, 2026.

Saleska et al., J Am Nutr Assoc 2024;43(1):1-11. RCT N=1,793. 15mg CBD + 5mg CBC vs CBD isolate for sleep disturbance (PROMIS SF-8A). No significant difference between CBC-augmented and CBD-alone arms. Null augmentation finding — CBC adds no measurable benefit to CBD for sleep at this dose. Effect size set conservatively (0.35) to reflect real-signal null evidence. Feb 27, 2026.
35 PubMed results. No human RCT or co-administration trial found. Evidence is preclinical (animal/in vitro), mechanistic, and reviews only. Null human combination search Feb 27, 2026.
12 PubMed results. No combination-specific human RCT found — results are reviews and meta-analyses mentioning both agents independently. Null search Feb 27, 2026.
17 PubMed results. No human RCT found. Evidence is preclinical and review articles only. Null human combination search Feb 27, 2026.
7 PubMed results. No human RCT of CBD+limonene combination found. Evidence is reviews and preclinical only. Null human combination search Feb 27, 2026.

7 PubMed results. No controlled CBD+linalool co-administration RCT found. One 2025 CBD-terpene sleep formulation trial noted but does not isolate linalool as independent variable. Null human combination search Feb 27, 2026.
